crush pen
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a small pen, or a drafting pen with a narrowing race, for confining and controlling animals for drenching, branding, etc; also called crush.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
